<div class="dealshub-about page-width" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 20px;">
  <style>
    .dealshub-about h1 { font-size:32px; font-weight:700; text-align:center; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .dealshub-about .about-subtitle { text-align:center; color:#666; margin-bottom:40px; font-size:16px; }
    .dealshub-about .about-section { margin-bottom:36px; }
    .dealshub-about .about-section h2 { font-size:22px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:12px; color:#111; }
    .dealshub-about .about-section p { font-size:15px; color:#444; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:12px; }
    .dealshub-about .about-values {
      display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr)); gap:20px; margin:32px 0;
    }
    .dealshub-about .value-card {
      background:#f9fafb; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; padding:24px; text-align:center;
    }
    .dealshub-about .value-card .icon { font-size:32px; margin-bottom:12px; display:block; }
    .dealshub-about .value-card h3 { font-size:16px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .dealshub-about .value-card p { font-size:13px; color:#666; line-height:1.6; margin:0; }
    .dealshub-about .about-cta {
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff5f5,#fef2f2); border:1px solid #fecaca;
      border-radius:16px; padding:32px; text-align:center; margin-top:40px;
    }
    .dealshub-about .about-cta h2 { font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .dealshub-about .about-cta p { color:#666; margin-bottom:16px; font-size:15px; }
    .dealshub-about .about-cta a {
      display:inline-block; padding:12px 32px; background:#e53e3e; color:#fff;
      border-radius:10px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; font-size:15px;
    }
    .dealshub-about .about-cta a:hover { background:#dc2626; }
  </style>

  <h1>About DealsHub</h1>
  <p class="about-subtitle">Your trusted destination for discovering amazing products at unbeatable prices.</p>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>DealsHub is a Miami-based online store dedicated to bringing you the best products from around the world. We carefully curate a wide selection of fashion, beauty, electronics, home essentials, and sports gear — all in one place, all at great prices.</p>
    <p>Our mission is simple: make quality products accessible and affordable for everyone in the United States, with a shopping experience you can trust.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
    <p>We combine the convenience of a one-stop shop with the value of global sourcing. Every product on our store is selected for quality, value, and customer satisfaction. We handle the logistics so you can focus on what matters — finding products you love.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-values">
    <div class="value-card">
      <span class="icon">&#x1F50D;</span>
      <h3>Curated Selection</h3>
      <p>We hand-pick products that offer real value, quality, and style from trusted global suppliers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <span class="icon">&#x1F4B0;</span>
      <h3>Best Prices</h3>
      <p>Our sourcing network lets us offer competitive prices you won't find at traditional retail.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <span class="icon">&#x1F6E1;&#xFE0F;</span>
      <h3>Secure Shopping</h3>
      <p>Every transaction is protected with industry-standard encryption and Shopify's secure checkout.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <span class="icon">&#x1F4E6;</span>
      <h3>Reliable Delivery</h3>
      <p>We partner with trusted shipping carriers to get your orders delivered safely and on time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Based in Miami</h2>
    <p>StyleHub Miami is proudly based in the heart of Miami, Florida. We serve customers across the United States with fast, reliable service and a team that genuinely cares about your experience.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-cta">
    <h2>Start Shopping Today</h2>
    <p>Discover trending products, exclusive deals, and everyday essentials.</p>
    <a href="/">Shop Now</a>
  </div>
</div>

